  <summary date="2019-08-27T17:58:20Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protect our Elections Act

This bill requires each state to annually certify that each entity that provides services related to any component of the state's election system meets certain criteria related to (1) the entity's ownership, and (2) compliance with cybersecurity best practices and incidence reporting requirements.</summary>
